84
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:01,680
What trick are you trying now?

85
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:08,879
Say it!

86
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:09,879
Say it!

87
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,800
I'm sorry.

88
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:15,600
My selfishness

89
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:17,839
caused your misunderstanding.

90
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,079
I only hope

91
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,639
it's not too late
to tell you the truth now.

92
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,600
It was because I trusted Nangong Xiao

93
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,800
that such a great disaster unfolded.

94
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,519
I killed Luo Ying.

95
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:37,639
I killed Wu too.

96
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:39,199
I'm sorry.

97
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,480
I'm sorry.

98
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:50,670
♪Sudden rain falls
and I get soaked alone♪

99
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:54,470
♪Even larks know where they belong♪

100
