102
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:07,959
I deserve this.

103
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:11,720
I deserve this.

104
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:12,920
But it's too late!

105
00:07:15,652 --> 00:07:16,800
It's too late.

106
00:07:17,236 --> 00:07:19,709
